column2: SELECT ALL   sa.OBJID AS akari_ID,   sa.RA AS akari_ra,   sa.DEC AS akari_dec,   SpecPhoto.z AS redshift,   SpecPhoto.zErr AS err_redshift,   SpecPhoto.class AS class   SpecPhoto.modelMag_u AS u,   SpecPhoto.modelMag_g AS g,   SpecPhoto.modelMag_r AS r,   SpecPhoto.modelMag_i AS i,   SpecPhoto.modelMag_z AS z,   SpecPhoto.modelMagErr_u AS uErr,   SpecPhoto.modelMagErr_g AS gErr,   SpecPhoto.modelMagErr_r AS rErr,   SpecPhoto.modelMagErr_i AS iErr,   SpecPhoto.modelMagErr_z AS zErr,      n.objid, n.distance into mydb.final_output        from MyDB.akari AS sa     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( sa.RA, sa.DEC, #) AS n
